\u00eb bot\u00ebn.","Fact19":"Lindy Hop  enjoyed a 1980's revival with the formation of organizations worldwide.","Fact2":"Savoy ishte nj\u00eb nd\u00ebr vendet e vetme t\u00eb koh\u00ebs q\u00eb lejonte hyrjen e njer\u00ebzve t\u00eb t\u00eb gjtiha racave.","Fact3":"Lindy Hop, nj\u00eb k\u00ebrcim i krijuar n\u00eb Savoy, vinte nga komuniteti afrikano-amerikan i Harlemit n\u00eb vitin 1928.","Fact4":"Salla Savoy ishte aq e njohur sa, n\u00eb dit\u00ebn e hapjes, duhej t\u00eb kthenin 2000 persona.","Fact5":"Salla e k\u00ebrcimit Savoy i mbylli dyert e saj n\u00eb korrik 1958, pas 32 vitesh.","Fact6":"Pista e k\u00ebrcimit ishte 15 me 60 metra. Kjo \u00ebsht\u00eb sa gjat\u00ebsia e nj\u00eb blloku t\u00eb t\u00ebr\u00eb apartamentesh!","Fact7":"Savoy p\u00ebr disa njihej si \"The Track\" (Pista) sepse pista e k\u00ebrcimit ishte shum\u00eb e gjat\u00eb dhe e holl\u00eb.","Fact8":"Hyrja n\u00eb sall\u00ebn Savoy kushtonte 30-85 cent p\u00ebr person. Kjo \u00ebsht\u00eb sa 6-16 USD sot!","Fact9":"Klubi kishte dy skena p\u00ebr grupet muzikore p\u00ebr t\u00eb luajtur muzik\u00eb pa ndalim. Nj\u00eb grup luante nd\u00ebrkoh\u00eb q\u00eb grupi tjet\u00ebr p\u00ebrgatitej.","Got It":"Fillo","How to Play":"E kuptova","MobileTutorial1":"Trokit butonat n\u00eb koh\u00eb me not\u00ebn.","MobileTutorial2":"Si t\u00eb luash","Mute":"\u00c7aktivizo","New Game":"Loj\u00eb e re","Next":"Para","One Player":"Dy lojtar\u00eb","Pause":"Pauz\u00eb","Paused":"N\u00eb pauz\u00eb","Replay":"Riluaj","Resume":"Vazhdo","Retry":"Riprovo","Score":"Rezultati: {{}}","Search":"K\u00ebrko","Share Facebook":"Ndaj n\u00eb Facebook","Share Twitter":"Ndaj n\u00eb Twitter","Share1":"Ndaj","Share2":"Lidhja u kopjua","ShareText":"Provo hapat e tu t\u00eb Lindy Hop n\u00eb pist\u00ebn e k\u00ebrcimit dhe provo ritmin t\u00ebnd n\u00eb loj\u00ebn me shum\u00eb lojtar\u00eb t\u00eb sotme t\u00eb #GoogleDoodle p\u00ebr t\u00eb festuar p\u00ebr k\u00ebrcimin \"swing\" dhe sall\u00ebn e k\u00ebrcimit Savoy!